{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"bf38c20b-d6ed-4ffc-af81-ef702e43edf8","content":"Yes, you'll hit **target framework compatibility issues**. MSTest v3 dropped support for end-of-life runtimes. Here's the breakdown:\n\n| Target | MSTest v3 Support |\n|---|---|\n| `net462` | ✅ Supported (≥ net462) |\n| `netcoreapp3.1` | ❌ Dropped — requires ≥ `net6.0` |\n| `net5.0` | ❌ Dropped — requires ≥ `net6.0` |\n\n**To migrate**, you'd need to update your unsupported TFMs to at least `net6.0` (or ideally `net8.0` LTS). You can also simplify the package references — MSTest v3 offers a single `MSTest` meta-package replacing the separate `MSTest.TestFramework` and `MSTest.TestAdapter` packages.\n\nWould you like me to update the project file for MSTest v3?","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"12b0350a-ebad-4922-9f1b-073073313b55","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user is multi-targeting `net5.0`, `net462`, and `netcoreapp3.1`. They want to migrate from MSTest v2 (2.2.10) to MSTest v3. Let me think about the compatibility issues:\n\nMSTest v3 has some important breaking changes and compatibility requirements:\n\n1. **Dropped TFM support**: MSTest v3 dropped support for several older target frameworks. Specifically:\n   - `.NET 5.0` is no longer supported (it's out of support from Microsoft)\n   - `.NET Core 3.1` is no longer supported (also out of support)\n   - `.NET Framework 4.6.2` is still supported, so that target should be fine\n\n. But `net5.0` and `netcoreapp3.1` won't work with MSTest v3 — they'd need to upgrade to at least `net6.0` or `net8.0`.\n\n2. **Package consolidation**: MSTest v3 consolidates the separate `MSTest.TestFramework` and `MSTest.TestAdapter` packages into a single `MSTest` meta-package, though the individual packages still exist.\n\n3. **Breaking API changes**: Some APIs were removed or changed in v3.\n\nThe core issue is that two of their three target frameworks are incompatible with MSTest v3, so they'd need to update those targets to a supported version.","outputTokens":764,"requestId":"1BD2:2912D8:AAF171:C0F999:6A03ECD7"},"id":"78a5591a-884b-406a-8abb-e1a6b636144c","timestamp":"2026-05-13T03:15:51.133Z","parentId":"00e54f7d-0940-4bf6-9e35-29fb317170c8"}
